Package com.platform.auth.internal

Class OAuth2UserInfo

java.lang.Object
com.platform.auth.internal.OAuth2UserInfo
@Entity public class OAuth2UserInfo extends Object
OAuth2 User Information entity storing user profile data from OAuth2 providers Contains standardized user information retrieved from Google, GitHub, Microsoft, etc.

This entity stores user information in a provider-agnostic format while preserving the original provider-specific data for audit and debugging purposes.
